cs.GT, cs.DS, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with optimization of allocation in guaranteed display advertising, which involves game theory (cs.GT), data structures (cs.DS), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions linear programming, which falls under cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), but it is not as relevant to the main focus of the paper as the other sub-categories.
